                        <h2>I Work With Small Business Consulting Them In Way's To Use Technology More Efficiently!</h2>
                        <p>Cloud infrastructure provides the necessary computational resources for training and deploying AI models.The start up I'm creating Cloud Technology Computing Corporation plans on leveraging a combination of Cloud Computing and AI to rapidly prototype and deploy innovative solutions in a cost efficient solution reducing upfront investment on things like hardware Previously, startups had to make significant investments in on-premises IT infrastructure and data centers. However, cloud computing provides resources that can be acquired as needed, eliminating the need for large upfront investments. According to a study by Deloitte, cloud technology can reduce IT costs by up to 40% for startups.I already have certifications in A.I and Cloud Computing.</p>
